text: Valeriy Georgievich Baych (25 August 1953 - 29 October 2020) was a Ukrainian politician, economist and businessman. He was born in Brody, Ukraine. From 1994 to 2002, he was a member of the Verkhovna Rada. Babych died of COVID-19 on 29 October 2020 at a hospital in Kyiv, Ukraine at the age of 67.Від коронавірусу помер Валерій Бабич – екснардеп і кандидат у президенти ==References== Category:1953 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Kyiv Category:Members of the Verkhovna Rada Category:Ukrainian businesspeople Category:Ukrainian economists
